abstract: NFL Roundup; Houston Texans quarterback Brian Hoyer may not play in upcoming game against New York Jets due to concussion; other football news noted.
lead_paragraph: Houston Texans quarterback Brian Hoyer missed practice Wednesday because of a concussion and is listed as questionable for Sunday’s game against the Jets.

headline.main: Concussion May Keep Hoyer Out vs. Jets
